{"tid":2168681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廣東陸豐疫情與香港流行毒株高度同源","createTime":"2020-08-22T02:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T15:09:14.000Z","uid":5195,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7a6fa3e39e3f80023baef5e396e02bdc6545a6b4","tid":2168681,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T02:38:59.000Z","msg":"8月22日，廣東省政府舉辦疫情防控新聞發佈會，省衛生健康委主任段宇飛介紹，疫情發生後，省衛生健康委會同省公安廳、深圳市、汕尾市以及省（市）疾控中心，開展病毒溯源，強化證據支撐，查清傳播脈絡。第一時間開展病毒全基因組測序，採取5例感染個案的鼻咽拭子樣本，對其病毒進行全基因組三代序列測定和分析，發現這5例的病毒基因序列高度同源。經與全球數據庫中的近8萬條新冠病毒全基因組序列進行比對分析，發現這5例同屬於香港本地流行的HK1分支，與香港流行毒株的病毒序列高度同源，同源百分率達99.99%。"},{"pid":"de29b9cbd8d65abd892b2b8eae82f7e1a74e10c3","tid":2168681,"uid":6604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T02:40:46.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎：反攻大陸去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f627b74bcc589d0cc5e294abd6175dd606bb26ef","tid":2168681,"uid":18477,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T02:41:00.000Z","msg":"即係坐大飛偷渡嗰班北姑雞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b8931aeaea465fc28d9bc43e26dfa94c4daa8e","tid":2168681,"uid":277339,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T02:43:14.000Z","msg":"香港政府拒絕封關危害國家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c94f25e8fe45393efe3ada44a9e57fd5bc86813","tid":2168681,"uid":318069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T02:43:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6261e120f4f55698084c699e0d10ab692de43023","tid":2168681,"uid":185121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T02:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />病毒都有愛國既"},{"pid":"08ffb6898383c2f696ece0918596bf580bbb1397","tid":2168681,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f627b74bcc589d0cc5e294abd6175dd606bb26ef","tid":2168681,"uid":18477,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"r